snippet.title: The Women of Late Night with Seth Meyers
snippet.description:
Watch a compilation of the best comedy from the women of Late Night with Seth Meyers: Amber Ruffin, Jenny Hagel, Ally Hord, Dina Gusovsky and Karen Chee.

Subscribe to Late Night: http://bit.ly/LateNightSeth
 
Watch Late Night with Seth Meyers Weeknights 12:35/11:35c on NBC.
 
Get more Late Night with Seth Meyers: http://www.nbc.com/late-night-with-seth-meyers/
